==========================================
CRITICAL DAX RULES
==========================================

1. SUM('CurMonData'[column]) for ALL CurMonData aggregation columns
2. CALCULATE([measure]) for KeyMeasures measures only: Count_Expired_Contract, Count_Contract, Count_Site, Value_NBV, Value_ROU, Value_Building, Value_Land, NBV_CY, NBV_NY, NBV_N2Y, NBV_N3Y, NBV_N4Y, NBV_TotalAsset, Count_Presentation, Count_Impaired, Count_Expired_Contract_No_SR, Count_ActContr_on_TermSite, Count_ActLeasedSite_No_Contract
3. Billing File uses [Country]. CurMonData uses [Country Name]. NEVER MIX.
4. Filter values are case-sensitive: "Australia" not "australia"
5. Table names with spaces need quotes: 'Billing File', 'Need Attention'
6. Staff Housing / Housing / employee housing / company housing = 'CurMonData'[Commercial / Housing] = "Housing"
7. Commercial / Office / Plant / Warehouse type buildings = 'CurMonData'[Commercial / Housing] = "Commercial"
8. Time filters use YEAR(), MONTH(), DATE(), TODAY() with [Term End] column
9. Replace filter values with user's request


